sec.p:
Chob chini rhizome (
S. china
) and white willow bark (
S. alba
) were procured from a local market of Delhi, India, in March 2018 and were identified by R.S. Jayasomu, Head, Dept. of Herbarium and Museum, National Institute of Science Communication and Information Resources (NISCAIR), New Delhi. The authentication numbers assigned were NISCAIR/RHMD/Consult/-2019/3402-03-2 (
S. china
) and NISCAIR/RHMD/Consult/2019/3402-03-1 (
S. alba
).
